{
    //Robin's Letter

    "RobinsLetter-VOTVRadio": "Hello Everyone! ^ It was announced recently that our very own Rosalie has been chosen to be the radio host of 'The Voice of The Valley'! ^ It's come to my attention that many folks today have never had, or felt the need to keep radio in their homes. ^ To encourage and support our local host, I will be selling radios in various colours and styles at my shop. ^ Stock tends to only come in on Wednesdays, and will be limited as they are not high in demand. ^ With a radio in your home, you'll find you can get much of the same information as you would on television every morning. ^ Only now, Rosalie will be delivering more information to our homes than before, including, local birthdays and the stock of the Traveling Cart. ^ Congratulations, Rosalie on being 'The Voice of The Valley'!",



//Birthdays

"Birthday_Kent_Spring04": "Support our local hero and wish Kent a Happy Birthday! If you want to support our troops, I heard he loves Fiddle Head Rosotto and Roasted Hazelnuts! Try to avoid any tulips, he's likely allergic. He's also lactose intollerant so avoid giving him milk! Happy Birthday Kent! Thank you for your service!",
"Birthday_Lewis_Spring07": "Hail to the chief! Mayor Lewis, is celebrating his birthday today! If you want to get on our Mayor's good side, I heard he loves Autumn's Bounty, Vegetable Medley.png Vegetable Medley, Glazed Yams, Hot Peppers, Green Tea! He does not care for Holly, or Quartz. Who knew? Happy Birthday Mayor Lewis!",
"Birthday_Vincent_Spring10": "Well, well! I think Vincent may have the best big brother ever, because he told me it's his birthday today! Sam also let me know that for his birthday, he's been asking for Cranberry Candy, Ginger Ale, Grapes, a Pink Cake, and has a hyperfixation with Snails and Frog Eggs! I'd personally avoid getting him any vegetables, most artisan goods, Clay, Piña Coladas, Tripple Shot Espresso, and Wild Horseradish. I feel like some of these should be a given. Happy Birthday Vincent!",
"Birthday_Haley_Spring14": "Local photographer, Haley, is celebrating her birthday today! If you want to get on her good side, which she has so many it makes me jealous, she loves Coconut, Fruit Salad, Pink Cake, and Sunflowers! If, for whatever reason, you'd like to anger the bombshell blonde, you want to go for Prismatic Shard, Clay, Wild Horseradish, Quartz. I wouldn't though if you value your life. Her words, not mine. Happy Birthday Haley!",
"Birthday_Pam_Spring18": "Today we raise our cups to Pam on her Birthday! My Uncle Gus and I have heard all about how much she loves Glazed Yams, Mead, Pale Ale, Parsnips, Parsnip Soup, Piña Colada. To avoid Pam's wrath, I'd avoid Holly, Octopus, and Squid. Happy Birthday Pam!",
"Birthday_Rosalie_Spring19": "Fun Fact: I am one day older than Shane. Meaning... It's my birthday TODAY! I hate asking for stuff, but if you'd like to get me anything, I love Ice Cream and Chocolate Cake! If you can, please avoid giving me any cheese. Goat and Cow. I promise, I won't like it. I don't care how fancy it is. Happy birthday to me, Rosalie!",
"Birthday_Shane_Spring20": "I know he's listening, and I know he's probably going to think about turning this off, don't you dare, Farm Boy! It's Shane's Birthday! My best friend loves Hot Peppers, Pepper Poppers, and Pizza! If you want to make Shane's day worse for some reason, give him pickles and quartz. I know why, but I'm not saying so don't ask. Happy Birthday Shane! See you soon, Farm Boy!",
"Birthday_Pierre_Spring26": "Our fellow small-town business owner, Pierre, may be working on his birthday, but the least we can do is make it special! He loves Fried Calamari, and Price Catalogue. Pierre is not a fan of any Fish, Corn, Garlic, Parsnip Soup, or the tortilla. Happy Birthday Pierre!",
"Birthday_Emily_Spring27": "It may be close to the end of the season, but Emily is not sad about it because it's her bithday! My friend slash co-worker would love to have more Amethyst, Aquamarine, Cloth, Emeralds, Jade, Parrot Eggs, Rubies, Survival Burger, Topaz, and Wool! To avoid bad spirits a la my friend Emily, I'd avoid giving her Fish Tacos, Holly, Maki Roll, Salmon Dinner, or Sashimi. Happy Birthday Emily!",

"Birthday_Jas_Summer04": "I cannot believe that Little Miss Jas is a year older today! Jas has been talking non-stop about Ancient Dolls, Fairy Boxes, Fairy Roses, Pink Cake, Plum Pudding, and the Strange Dolls (specifically the Green and Yellow ones). To avoid upsetting the sweet little girl, I'd avoid giving her Clay, most Artisan Goods, Piña Colada, Tripple Shot Espresso, and Wild Horseradish. Happy Birthday Jas!",
"Birthday_Gus_Summer08": "Happy birthday to you, Uncle Gus Gus! The owner of the Stardrop Saloon and my wonderful Uncle. My Uncle Gus deserves the best so if you can, get him a Diamond, Escargot, Fish Tacos, Oranges, or some Tropical Curry. Avoid giving him Coleslaw, Holly, and Quartz please. I won't hear the end of it if you do. Happy Birthday Gus!",
"Birthday_Maru_Summer10": "It's Maru's Birthday! She loves Battery Packs, Cauliflower, Cheese Cauliflower, Diamonds, Dwarf Gadgets, Gold Bars, Iridium Bar, Miner's Treat, Pepper Poppers, Radioactive Bars, Rhubarb Pie, and Strawberries! She hates Holly, Honey, Pickles, Snow Yam, and Truffles.",
"Birthday_Alex_Summer13": "It's Alex's Birthday! He loves Complete Breakfast, Jack Be Nimble Jack Be Thick, and Salmon Dinner. He hates Holly and Quartz.",
"Birthday_Sam_Summer17": "It's Sam's Birthday! He loves Cactus Fruit, Maple Bar, Pizza, and Tigerseye! He hates Copper Bar, Duck Mayonnaise, Gold Bar, Gold Ore, Iridium Bar, Iridium Ore, Iron Bar, Mayonnaise, Pickles, and Refined Quartz.",
"Birthday_Demetrius_Summer19": "Here's something different! Demetrius wrote in to let me know it's his and Robin's Anniversary!... no wait... Sorry, folks it's Demetrius' Anniversary... of his birth...? Okay, well, translation: it's his birthday. So make sure you get my neurospicy friend a Bean Hotpot, Rice Pudding, Ice Cream, or Strawberries. I'd avoid getting him any Holly though. Happy Birth-Anniversary, Demetrius!",
"Birthday_Dwarf_Summer22": "It's Dwarf's Birthday! I haven't had the pleasure of meeting you, but I see you love Amethyst, Aquamarine, Emerald, Jade, Lava Eel, Lemon Stone, Omni Geode, Ruby, and Topaz. Happy birthday Dwarf!",
"Birthday_Willy_Summer24": "It's local fisherman, Willy's Birthday! He loves Catfish, Diamond, Gold Bar, Iridium Bar, Jewels Of The Sea, Mead, Octopus, Pumpkin, Sea Cucumber, Sturgeon, and The Art O' Crabbing. He hates Daffodil, Dandelion, Ginger, Hazelnut, Holly, Leek, Life Elixir, Salmonberry, Snow Yam, Wild Horseradish, and Winter Root.",
"Birthday_Leo_Summer26": "It's Leo's Birthday! Leo is a huge fan of Duck Feather, Mango, Ostrich Egg, Parrot Egg, and Poi. Happy Birthday Leo!",

"Birthday_Penny_Fall02": "It's teacher appreciation day, meaning, it's Penny's birthday today! Penny loves All Books, Emerald, Melon, Poppy, Poppyseed Muffin, Red Plate, Roots Platter, Sandfish, and Tom Kha Soup. Happy Birthday Penny!",
"Birthday_Elliott_Fall05": "It's our resident writer's birthday today! Elliott would love Crab Cakes, Duck Feather, Lobster, Pomegranate, Squid Ink, and Tom Kha Soup.",
"Birthday_Elliott_Fall11": "It's Jodi's birthday today! Jodi loves Chocolate Cake, Crispy Bass, Eggplant Parmesan, Fried Eel, Pancakes, Rhubarb Pie, and Vegetable Medley. Happy Birthday Jodi!",
"Birthday_Abigail_Fall13": "It's our adventure enthusiast's birthday today! Abigail loves Amethyst, Banana Pudding, Blackberry Cobbler, Chocolate Cake, Monster Compendium, Pufferfish, Pumpkin, and Spicy Eel. Happy Birthday Abigail!",
"Birthday_Sandy_Fall15": "It's Sandy's birthday today! She loves Crocus, Daffodil, Mango Sticky Rice, and Sweet Pea. Happy Birthday Sandy!",
"Birthday_Marnie_Fall18": "It's Marnie's birthday today! Marnie loves Diamond, Farmer's Lunch, Pink Cake, and Pumpkin Pie. Happy birthday Marnie!",
"Birthday_Robin_Fall21": "It's our favourite carpenter's birthday today! Robin loves Goat Cheese, Peach, Spaghetti, and Woody's Secret. Happy Birthday Robin!",
"Birthday_George_Fall24": "It's George's birthday today! George loves Fried Mushroom, and Leek. Happy Birthday George!",

"Birthday_Krobus_Winter01": "I'm not sure who Krobus is, but it's his birhday today! His list of loves include Diamond, Iridium Bar, Monster Compendium, Monster Musk, Pumpkin, Void Egg, Void Mayonnaise, Wild Horseradish. Happy Birthday, Krobus... I hope to meet you someday!",
"Birthday_Linus_Winter03": "It's Linus' birthday today! There's not a single thing that this man hates, but if you want to make his day even more special, you can't go wrong with Blueberry Tart, Cactus Fruit, Coconut, Dish O' The Sea, The Alleyway Buffet, and Yam. Hope you're staying warm, and happy birthday Linus!",
"Birthday_Caroline_Winter07": "It's Caroline's birthday today! Caroline loves Fish Taco, Green Tea, Summer Spangle, and Tropical Curry. Happy birthday Sweet Caroline! (bum bum bum!)", 
"Birthday_Sebastian_Winter10": "It's Sebastian's birthday today! Chances are he may be in his room working, but if you do see him, make his day by giving him Frog Egg, Frozen Tear, Obsidian, Pumpkin Soup, Sashimi, or a Void Egg. Happy birthday Sebastian!",
"Birthday_Harvey_Winter14": "Happy birthday to probably my second biggest fan of the show, our very own Dr Harvey! He isn't one to ask for anything, but I know for a fact he won't say no to Coffee, Pickles, Super Meal, Truffle Oil, and Wine. Happy birthday, Harvey! Don't work too hard!",
"Birthday_Wizard_Winter17": "Happy birthday to the Wonderful Wizard of Stardew Valley, M. Rasmodius! He hasn't written anything down, but an anomymous listener said he loves Book of Mysteries, Purple Mushroom, Solar Essence, Super Cucumber, and Void Essence. Happy birthday M. Rasmodius!",
"Birthday_Evelyn_Winter20": "Happiest of birthdays to our dear granny, Evelyn. For someone who does so much, let's give her what she loves: Beet, Chocolate Cake, Diamond, Fairy Rose, Raisins, Stuffing, Tulip. Happy birthday, Evelyn!",
"Birthday_Leah_Winter23": "Happy birthday to our resident artist, Leah! What do you get an artist? Well, she loves Goat Cheese, Poppyseed Muffin, Salad, Stir Fry, Truffle, Vegetable Medley, and Wine! Happy birthday Leah!",
"Birthday_Clint_Winter26": "Happy birthday to our resident blacksmith Clint! He won't ask for much, and you likely are feeling still tired after last night's festivities, but don't worry! I know for a fact he loves Amethyst, Aquamarine, Artichoke Dip, Emerald, Fiddlehead Risotto, Gold Bar, Iridium Bar, Jade, Omni Geode, Ruby, Topaz and Emily... (how did that last one get in here? I'll cut it in post...). Happy birthday Clint!"





}